Students


Search Handshake






Search Handshake
Internships and jobs for UIC students
All UIC students have a Handshake account -- just log in with your UIC netID and password!
Handshake is an online job board that can only be used by students and alumni at Handshake member schools, including UIC. Employers post internships, co-ops and full-time positions year-round on Handshake. On-campus positions at both the East and West campuses are posted to the site as well.
Make the most of Handshake

Update your profile because employers can discover your profile and message you on Handshake.
Apply for on-campus jobs, internships, and full-time jobs.
Upload your resume to Handshake so you can easily apply.
Register for employer events and career fairs.
Book individual career advising appointments through Handshake.






Claim your account to get started!






